data.description: Welcome home! Charming one-story home with 4 bedrooms, 2 baths, & a 2 car garage. This home features a chef-ready kitchen and adjacent breakfast room that overlooks the front yard landscaping. Homeowners will enjoy the master retreat with its soaker tub and separate shower, a large walk-in closet, and direct access to the backyard. Additionally, the Pecos includes a flex room may be used as a formal dining room, a home office, or a fourth bedroom! This home wont last long!
